41:27.971 --> 41:29.975
in the history
of automatic lights,

41:29.975 --> 41:31.077
yours automatically

41:31.077 --> 41:32.379
didn't come on,

41:32.379 --> 41:33.783
'cause sometimes...
Roger, Roger.

